				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Greetings,
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Kormok Paynegrinder wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">However a tip to add would be that unlike mage/necro our pets have no "natural" agro ie warder can run thru mobs behind ya and nothing happens but pets will have a string of hatred waiting for the master to stop to unleash the whirlwind.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
